title: O'Neill - Surf de Nuit 2012 Trailer
description:
O'Neill Surf de Nuit 2012 takes place at Anglet, France August 16th and 17th, presented by Philips and Orangina, powered by Desperados.
Free Surfing and Stand Up Paddle Course, free concerts presented by the Da Brasilians YES FM, Kid Bombardos and Hushpuppies. Night surfing contest with some of the best surfers in the world.
